Coie, J. D., Dodge, K. A., & Coppotelli, H.(1982). Dimensions and types of social status: A cross-age perspective. Developmental Psychology, 18, 557-570.\cr
Coie, J.D., & Dodge, K.A. (1983). Continuities and changes in children's social status: A five-year longitudinal study. Merril-Palmer Quarterly, 29, 261-282.\cr
Newcomb, A. F., & Bukowski, W. M. (1983). Social impact and social preference as determinants of children's peer group status. Developmental Psychology, 19, 856-867.\cr
Maassen, G. H. and Landsheer, J. A. (1998). SSRAT: The processing of rating scales for the determination of two-dimensional sociometric status. Behavior Research Methods Instruments &amp; Computers, 30(4), 674-679.
}
